🔑 Key Features
🎯 Live Ambulance Tracking
Update and broadcast ambulance location every few seconds (simulate or use mobile GPS)

Display markers on a map

🏥 ICU/Bed Monitoring
Admin can update bed availability in real time

Display dashboard with filters (location-wise, emergency load)

🔔 Real-time Emergency Alerts
Alert page shows new cases as they are added

SignalR used for push notifications to browser UI

Mark alert as resolved

📍 Map Dashboard (Frontend)
Display:

Ambulances with availability color codes

Hospitals with bed capacity

Active emergencies with warning icons
